{"tid":695254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金融史上最正銀行妺　宅男走出家門「去存錢」","createTime":"2018-06-09T04:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T06:07:17.000Z","uid":72009,"like":592,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"934176631a18e9307e87ae7a0fecf20672164a1c","tid":695254,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"能讓宅男走出家門的，恐怕只有「野性的呼喚」了！<br />\n網友在臉書社團爆廢公社PO文，他前往銀行辦理業務，驚見一名外型神似日本女星波多野結衣的超級正妹，就站在櫃檯裡。<br />\n<br />\n對方笑容可掬地問他需要辦理什麼業務，原PO趁機撩妹：「我想在您這裡存放我的心。」<br />\n沒想到妹子處變不驚，神回「不好意思！我們這裡是銀行，不辦理器官存放喔！」<br />\n原PO頓時像被厚頭龍撞上，說不出話來，原地結巴，場面尷尬。<br />\n網友大笑，誇這位櫃檯小姐太有智慧了，一句話四兩撥千斤，讓「存心哥」碰了個超級軟釘子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_52b21e9c9dad6570535e3f1b160eea3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180609%2F640_52b21e9c9dad6570535e3f1b160eea3e.jpg&h=144f7f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180609/640_3a9f913fb11722aa4f152947b4c6e870.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180609%2F640_3a9f913fb11722aa4f152947b4c6e870.jpg&h=52a12b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 銀行av"},{"pid":"d8e53ebc856b27af5693627258f59b9327a9f5f9","tid":695254,"uid":49004,"like":141,"dislike":3,"score":138,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"個look似泉水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1433a7f9c72116c8dec3e2b8d589c48cfa55c433","tid":695254,"uid":2638,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11cab28d0cf99b4d1fa7699cc285c227cbe14e2","tid":695254,"uid":60785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T04:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa